LibrarySystem.LibraryAdmin
Enclosing class:
LibrarySystem
public class LibrarySystem.LibraryAdmin
extends java.lang.Object
When the administrator enters the system with a password, he will be able to add books, delete books, update information.

    • searchByAuthor

      public void searchByAuthor​(java.lang.String author)
      Search whole library by author name. When searching by author name, all books of the author in the library will be listed on the screen. Then, whichever book the user chooses, the location(s) of that book will be displayed.
      Parameters:
      author - author's name

    • searchByTitle

      public void searchByTitle​(java.lang.String title)
      Search whole library by book title. When searching by book title, author name, location and status will be shown
      Parameters:
      title - Book's title
